DRESS TO KILL and DEFINITE ARTICLE get a 10/10 on video and audio. GLORIOUS is a touch grainy and UNREPEATABLE a bit grainier. But all four of these shows are absolutely amazing and should be downloaded at all costs. Eddie at his best! LIVE AT THE AMBASSADOR'S is also a fabulous bit of work but the video quality and the overall basic environment're a dampener. But for an Eddie fan, that shouldn't be a problem. CIRCLE and SEXIE although are very good quality prints but the shows aren't quite up there.  Download the last two only if you have nothing else to download. 
And Krillian, I can't begin to say how grateful i am to you for this beautiful up. Thank god for people like you. Cheers mate!
@ shanialowe: I aim to please :) I had a hard time getting all the shows, and as an act of mercy I decided to seed 'em ^^ glad you guys like it!

hi there!  i love Eddie Izzard, but i have a couple of these already.  how do I download just a couple of these fome Azureus Vuse? i know theres a way, but im too 'tarded to figure it out myself.  any help would be appreciated.  A LOT. thanks again for putting this up, krillian.

DJDrumish, click on the "Advanced" tab, double-click the name of the torrent, click the "Files" tab, right-click on the files you do NOT want to download, select "set priority" and then select "do not download" or "delete." Either one will stop the file from being downloaded.
